      "created_at": "2020-01-07T18:39:42.524Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Kam dy endrra te bukura<br>\nNje e kam per vete , nje e kam per ty<br>\nKaq shume u deshen kto endrra<br>\nSaqe u perqafuan<br>\nAq shume u perqafuan, saqe u puthen<br>\nAq shume u puthen<br>\nSaqe linden dy femije</p>\n<p>Kaq shpejt I rriten femijet<br>\nSaqe ata kishin endrra<br>\nKaq endrra te bukura kishin<br>\nSaqe u dashuruan<br>\nAq shume u dashuruan<br>\nSaqe u puthen<br>\nKaq shume u puthen<br>\nSaqe linden kater femije</p>\n<p>Tani kam vetem nje enderr<br>\nEshte e jotja<br>\nPer ty<br>\nMerre</p>\n<p>XhaTani - Cerrik Maj 1999</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
      "like_count": 0
    },
