      "created_at": "2020-01-07T20:39:47.916Z",
      "cooked": "<p><a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/alba2265\">@Alba2265</a>, meqe shof qe po merresh me probleme linguistike. Po e gjete se kush osht rrenja e perbashket e ketyre dy termave pellazgjike:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>shejton = shenjtor</p>\n</blockquote>",
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
      "like_count": 0
    },
